Slice up @red chillies{} and @green chillies{}.

==Chilli sauce==
Add chillies to a #bowl{} with @vinegar{}, @salt{}, @brown sugar{} and mix up.

==Mayo==
Dice up @onion{}, mix in a #bowl{} with @mayo{}, @hot sauce{}, @lemon{}, @black pepper{}, @salt{}.

==Burgers==
Grill @burger buns{} until toasted.

Grill @beef burgers{} for ~{2-3%minutes} per side.

Add @cheese{} on last ~{2%minutes}.

Add mayo to bun.

Add chillies on top.
